---
title: Cheesy Greek-Style Honey & Oregano Halloumi with Roasted Veggie Couscous
description: A medley of brightly coloured veggies and big flavours like garlic and herbs are super filling, while still feeling fresh and light. A
drizzle of sweet honey tops off a dish whose star, really, is the salty, moreish halloumi – it’s outrageously good!
